honorificSuffix">MD, PhD</span></a> <a class="orcid-id" href="https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5998-9034" property="identifier" aria-label="ORCID identifier" target="_blank">https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5998-9034</a></span></span></span><a href="#tab-contributors" class="to-authors-affiliations" data-id="article-authors-viewall">Authors Info &amp; Affiliations</a></div><div class="core-self-citation"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span class="heading">Publication</span>: <span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">41</span></span><span class="delimiter">, </span><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">7</span></span></div><div class="doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.2021210063" property="sameAs">https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.2021210063</a></div></div><div class="core-relations my-3"><div class="relation mb-3"><div class="relation--head"><i class="icon-info"></i><a href="/doi/10.1148/rg.229005">Correction(s) for this article</a></div></div></div><div class="info-panel"><div class="info-panel__left-content"><div class="info-panel__metrics info-panel__item"></div></div><div class="info-panel__right-content"><div class="info-panel__article_tools info-panel__item">



        
