453.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.7150/jca.5187">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23193431/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Primary+anorectal+melanoma%3A+an+update&amp;author=P+Carcoforo&amp;author=MT+Raiji&amp;author=GM+Palini&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=J+Cancer&amp;pages=449-453&amp;doi=10.7150%2Fjca.5187&amp;pmid=23193431">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Hayward NK, Wilmott JS, Waddell N, et al. Whole-genome landscapes of major melanoma subtypes. <em>Nature</em> 2017;545(7653):175–180.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/nature22071">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28467829/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Whole-genome+landscapes+of+major+melanoma+subtypes&amp;author=NK+Hayward&amp;author=JS+Wilmott&amp;author=N+Waddell&amp;publication_year=2017&amp;journal=Nature&amp;pages=175-180&amp;doi=10.1038%2Fnature22071&amp;pmid=28467829">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Nassar KW, Tan AC. The mutational landscape of mucosal melanoma. <em>Semin Cancer Biol</em> 2020;61:139–148.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.semcancer.2019.09.013">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31655118/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google